OL,3,C'My daughter took her own life seven
OL,4,Chours after getting university result'
OL,6,FA family from Anglesey who lost their
OL,7,Fdaughter to suicide four years ago are
OL,8,Fcalling on universities to provide
OL,9,Fbetter duty of care for their students.
OL,11,FMared Foulkes died in July 2020, seven
OL,12,Fhours after receiving her results from
OL,13,FCardiff University.
OL,15,FThese indicated that she had failed
OL,16,Fone assessment and would not be able
OL,17,Fto continue into her third year,
OL,18,Fdespite the fact that she had re-sat
OL,19,Fher exam and passed.
