OL,3,C'My daughter took her own life seven
OL,4,Chours after getting university result'
OL,6,F"She was very conscientious, and she
OL,7,Fwent to university to succeed,"
OL,8,FMared's mum Iona said.
OL,10,FHours after receiving an email with
OL,11,Fher results, 21-year-old Mared took
OL,12,Fher own life.
OL,14,F"She left that day believing she had
OL,15,Ffailed the year and wasn't able to go
OL,16,Fback to Cardiff," Iona Foulkes told
OL,17,FS4C's current affairs programme, Y Byd
OL,18,Far Bedwar.
OL,20,F"We have never been the same again.
OL,21,FThis family unit has gone forever."
