OL,3,C'My daughter took her own life seven
OL,4,Chours after getting university result'
OL,6,FThe family say the result Mared
OL,7,Freceived was misleading, and wrongly
OL,8,Fstated that she was unable to continue
OL,9,Fwith her studies.
OL,11,FAt the inquest into Mared's death in
OL,12,FOctober 2021, the coroner said the way
OL,13,FCardiff University communicated the
OL,14,Fresults was "complex and confusing".
OL,16,F"They've lost a student, but I've lost
OL,17,Fa very, very sweet girl," Iona said.
OL,19,F"I have to pass her grave every day,
OL,20,Fdo (Cardiff University) have to do
OL,21,Fthat?"
