OL,3,C'My daughter took her own life seven
OL,4,Chours after getting university result'
OL,6,FCampaigning for better duty of care to
OL,7,Fstudents at university
OL,9,FIona and the family are part of the
OL,10,F'For the 100' campaign, a group of
OL,11,Ffamilies calling for better duty of
OL,12,Fcare for students from their
OL,13,Funiversities. The '100' represents the
OL,14,Fnumber of students who die by suicide
OL,15,Fevery year in Britain.
OL,17,FWith the help of lawyers, Iona has
OL,18,Fcreated a report with recommendations
OL,19,Ffor universities to try to prevent
OL,20,Fstudent suicides.
