OL,3,C'My daughter took her own life seven
OL,4,Chours after getting university result'
OL,6,FRecommendations include improving the
OL,7,Fway universities communicate with
OL,8,Ffamilies about their children's mental
OL,9,Fhealth, and an 'opt-out' system if
OL,10,Fstudents do not want their parents to
OL,11,Fknow about any serious wellbeing
OL,12,Fconcerns.
OL,14,F"Currently, the confidentiality law
OL,15,Frestricts universities from contacting
OL,16,Fthe family if a serious welfare or
OL,17,Fmental health situation arises," said
OL,18,Fsolicitor Dr Emma Roberts, who has
OL,19,Fhelped the family write the report.
