OL,3,C'My daughter took her own life seven
OL,4,Chours after getting university result'
OL,6,F"We want to see the consistency from
OL,7,Fone university to another, and only by
OL,8,Fchanging the law can that happen."
OL,10,FNine months before Mared died, she had
OL,11,Fvisited University Support Services to
OL,12,Fdiscuss her mental health. The family
OL,13,Fwere unaware of this for a year
OL,14,Ffollowing her death.
OL,16,FFor Iona Foulkes, the lack of
OL,17,Fcommunication from the university was
OL,18,F"shocking".
