OL,6,FA spokesperson for Cardiff University
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are very sorry that the
OL,8,Ffamily feels that we have shown a lack
OL,9,Fof sympathy ` that was never our
OL,10,Fintention. We know the family feel we
OL,11,Fcould have done things differently and
OL,12,Fwe have apologised for where we did
OL,13,Fnot get things right."
