OL,3,C'My daughter took her own life seven
OL,4,Chours after getting university result'
OL,6,FFollowing the inquest into Mared's
OL,7,Fdeath, they said they wanted to
OL,8,F"improve the tone and language of all
OL,9,Four written communications to our
OL,10,Fstudents", and that the practice of
OL,11,Fusing a notional or estimated mark to
OL,12,Frecord an academic 'fail' where a
OL,13,Fstudent has not met a competency
OL,14,Fstandard had been stopped with
OL,15,Fimmediate effect.
