OL,6,FThey have since revised their
OL,7,Fprocesses to ensure the university is
OL,8,Fas "open and transparent as possible
OL,9,Fin responding to questions that may
OL,10,Farise from family and friends,
OL,11,Frecognising there may be limits to
OL,12,Fthis where there is a police
OL,13,Finvestigation and coroner's inquest.
OL,15,FThey said they respect the family's
OL,16,Fcalls for an 'opt-out' system and are
OL,17,Fcontinuing to review this as part of
OL,18,Ftheir current review into their
OL,19,FUniversity Mental Health and Suicide
OL,20,FSafety strategies.
